    {
      "id": "PopularPost34353",
      "post_content": "The Portal version of [Hidden Horror](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hidden Horror).  \nBig advantage: [Knight subtype regarding tribal use](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=122045).  \nRegarding Oracle change it's also funny to know how the \"trigger only when hardcast\" restriction used to be profitable in that manner.  \nRegarding the former Mercenary synergy, [Cateran Summons](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cateran Summons) should also find use in such a knight deck for aforementioned reasons, especially since this card as well as Haakon synergize with [changeling](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=changeling) spells including stuff like [Nameless Inversion](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nameless Inversion).",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost34353\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">The Portal version of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hidden Horror\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hidden Horror\">Hidden Horror</a>.<br/>Big advantage: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"122045\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=122045\">Knight subtype regarding tribal use</a>.<br/>Regarding Oracle change it's also funny to know how the \"trigger only when hardcast\" restriction used to be profitable in that manner.<br/>Regarding the former Mercenary synergy, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Cateran Summons\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cateran Summons\">Cateran Summons</a> should also find use in such a knight deck for aforementioned reasons, especially since this card as well as Haakon synergize with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"changeling\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=changeling\">changeling</a> spells including stuff like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Nameless Inversion\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nameless Inversion\">Nameless Inversion</a>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '34353'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy416\">Mode</span>\r\n                 