      "id": "PopularPost183955",
      "post_content": "Completely unjustifiable oracle wording change. The drawback was only meant to trigger when played from the hand, it's as clear as day on the face of the card. What's the matter Wizards, afraid Mercenary decks are going to start running roughshod over Legacy if this guy had his correct wording? I suppose this *would* be more broken than Time Vault if you allowed it to be played how it was printed. ",
